        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 14. Aboral cups of type series of Globulocrinus amphoraformis n. gen., n. sp. from Réqui. A–I: lateral views showing variations and changes in morphology during ontogeny, G: holotype (MNHN.F.A82011); A–F, H–L: paratypes (MNHN. F.A82012), A: paratype 1, B: paratype 2, C and K–L: paratype 3, D: paratype 4, E: paratype 5, F: paratype 6, H: paratype 7, I: paratype 8, J: distal face of radial circlet of paratype 9; K–L: aboral views of basal circlet of paratype 3, showing pentagonal depression corresponding to stalk insertion. Scale bar equals 0.5 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4700758/files/figure.png" .

